Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.21,0:02:14.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,进入9月  第二学期开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.21,0:02:14.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs20}注：日本的学校多采用三学期制  第二学期一般为9到12月
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.46,0:02:20.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,忘掉君岛晃的事情吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.30,0:02:23.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么要忘掉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.47,0:02:26.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你听清楚了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.87,0:02:35.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是打算警告我吗  这反而更让我在意了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.38,0:02:40.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过  美纱姐果然知道君岛晃的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.35,0:02:47.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下面是报告书No.4的FLAG
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.75,0:02:52.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,1.  已经发现了君岛报告书No.3
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.80,0:03:03.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,2.  把在种子岛的4处推荐地点拍摄的火箭升空照片上传至IRUO.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.61,0:03:11.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,3.  用贴了地理标签的火枪试射一次以上
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.74,0:03:20.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,4.  按下存放在机器人诊所的五二郎君的启动按钮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.84,0:03:30.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五二郎君是什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.75,0:03:34.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机器人诊所不就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.03,0:03:42.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,注意  今天开始就要在这里组建Gun制造2号机啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.47,0:03:47.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎  对方愿意把这里借给我们吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.32,0:03:54.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  我想只要有工作人员在场就没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.41,0:03:59.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这里还有起重机  空着不用也有点浪费
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.56,0:04:03.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这次可以在站立的情况下进行组装哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.87,0:04:05.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呜呼呼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.70,0:04:07.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我燃起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.64,0:04:10.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连用哪种驱动系统都还没定下来呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.17,0:04:16.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  关于这一点其实还是想请教一下DOKU
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.50,0:04:20.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,连同磁单…  的事情一起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.72,0:04:22.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你还没有放弃吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.70,0:04:26.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为那个最终话泄漏的事件
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.84,0:04:29.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,世间对于Gunvarrel的评价一下子就跌到了谷底
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.74,0:04:32.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们要完成Gun制造2号机
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.13,0:04:33.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然后想想办法才行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.93,0:04:34.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.11,0:04:36.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么了  淳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.62,0:04:37.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.64,0:04:42.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  不…不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.15,0:04:49.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂  啊  是爸爸啊  我现在和朋友在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.20,0:04:52.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎！？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.49,0:04:58.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\move(393,152,518,152)\fs18\bord0}公\N立\N种\N子\N岛\N医\N院
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.21,0:05:06.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,115)\fs18\1c000000\bord0\b1}重症监护病房（ICU）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.29,0:05:19.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？  请问你有什么事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.59,0:05:27.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎  那  那个  我…  我是藤田爷爷的孙女
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.31,0:05:29.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,…来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.05,0:05:42.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回来…回到我的身边…笑一笑吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.44,0:05:45.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.09,0:05:51.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.19,0:05:52.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,淳
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.25,0:05:53.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.51,0:05:55.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,DOKU他怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.58,0:05:58.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我没能见到他
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.07,0:06:00.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.76,0:06:02.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,难道说是谢绝探望吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.80,0:06:03.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.55,0:06:08.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为他不愿意见我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.20,0:06:14.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.92,0:06:16.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你见过DOKU了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.02,0:06:19.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  我昨天去看望过他了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.81,0:06:20.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.36,0:06:23.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前天淳去探病的时候却没能见到
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.31,0:06:27.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以他现在怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.40,0:06:29.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  好像有点虚弱
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.24,0:06:32.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不光身体虚弱  情绪上也很消沉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.34,0:06:34.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,情绪消沉？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.21,0:06:37.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我正在考虑要不要把店给关了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.45,0:06:40.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是时候该收手了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.43,0:06:43.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会这样
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.30,0:06:59.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你居然会出现在这里  真是少见
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.98,0:07:05.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是不是在为不敢去医院而感到消沉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.86,0:07:12.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那倒不是  本来我和藤田爷爷的关系就不是那么亲密
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.06,0:07:14.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.13,0:07:16.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.47,0:07:21.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…  我在考虑要不要退出Robo部
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.56,0:07:24.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你来这招吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.36,0:07:27.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯  这还真是让人头疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.51,0:07:30.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之  要不要先进店里坐坐
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.58,0:07:35.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是的  你这个大嘴巴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.12,0:07:37.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀  我一不小心就…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.56,0:07:42.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不会又是去多管什么奇怪的闲事了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.25,0:07:42.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.44,0:07:45.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起这个  你得到情报了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.13,0:07:48.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(320,325)\fs16}宇宙开发事业团
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.13,0:07:48.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,DOKU是前NASDA的技术人员
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.14,0:07:52.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,NASDA  就是指那个JAXA的前身吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.46,0:07:53.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,没错
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.39,0:07:57.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,18年前  刚开业的机器人诊所是间面向小孩子的店
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.32,0:08:02.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,店门口摆满了DOKU制造的机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.33,0:08:04.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也记得很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.97,0:08:11.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当时DOKU常说
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.22,0:08:16.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机器人是人类的好朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.54,0:08:17.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.50,0:08:20.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是难以置信
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.58,0:08:23.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么  那些机器人哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.22,0:08:26.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在机器人诊所里沉眠着呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.49,0:08:28.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.53,0:08:30.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为发生了事故
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.14,0:08:32.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.28,0:08:39.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…  抱歉我先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.23,0:08:41.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小淳？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.57,0:08:49.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,11年前  有个小孩子被机器人压倒  受了伤
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.79,0:08:55.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那个孩子就是DOKU的孙女  大德淳和
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.83,0:09:05.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好  我的名字叫做与四郎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.54,0:09:07.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是大家的朋友——机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.36,0:09:10.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}来和我握握手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.85,0:09:10.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我们才不是朋友呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.13,0:09:15.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}你好  我是大家的朋友——机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.79,0:09:14.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你才不是我的朋友…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.86,0:09:22.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋  你在想些什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.20,0:09:26.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看看你都干了些什么  干了些什么！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.25,0:09:33.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吗  所以淳才会害怕机器人…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.64,0:09:37.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你打算怎么办  小亚希
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.65,0:09:46.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还是算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.26,0:09:49.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我听说了DOKU的机器人们的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.17,0:09:53.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我们修好它们  给DOKU打打气吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.51,0:09:55.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.12,0:09:59.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,淳你也想让DOKU恢复精神对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.82,0:10:02.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我也想…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.79,0:10:04.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为你害怕机器人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.89,0:10:06.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你想要退出Robo部也是因为这个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.52,0:10:09.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什么意思  我可没听说过啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.03,0:10:11.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,八  八汐同学
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.86,0:10:13.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是怎么回事  淳
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.67,0:10:17.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我  我之所以进入Robo部
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.13,0:10:21.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是单纯地想找个能代替空手道的活动来打发时间
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.41,0:10:24.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使我的空手道很差劲  但我也能坚持下去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.43,0:10:26.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我很喜欢它
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.34,0:10:29.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是  机器人就…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.99,0:10:31.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然还是会害怕吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.98,0:10:33.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.70,0:10:39.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么…  我是绝对不会允许淳退出的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.54,0:10:40.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.01,0:10:46.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,直到你能喜欢上机器人的某一处为止  我是绝对不会放你走的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.33,0:10:47.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.59,0:10:50.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,走吧  这是部长的命令
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.67,0:10:52.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呜哇  小亚希？  哇
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.29,0:10:58.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.54,0:11:06.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不知道还能启动吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.28,0:11:12.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.91,0:11:16.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an7\fs20\fad(2000,0)}注：GOJIRO是五二郎的日文罗马音
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.97,0:11:18.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.39,0:11:20.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.60,0:11:24.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,线缆被切断了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.00,0:11:32.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这些机器人是被DOKU自己亲手「杀死」的吗
Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,//------------------TXTB-------------------
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.45,0:11:39.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,八  八汐同学呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.64,0:11:41.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他正在里面修理五二郎君
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.78,0:11:43.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呜啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.21,0:11:47.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说无论如何都想要修好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.58,0:11:50.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加油  加油  大哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.62,0:11:52.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等这孩子修好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.66,0:11:56.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,淳能不能当一下操作员呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.43,0:11:56.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.81,0:12:00.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得只有淳才能胜任
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.69,0:12:03.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拜托你了  淳
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.39,0:12:05.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呜…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.92,0:12:11.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好  这样应该就没问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.34,0:12:13.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.74,0:12:14.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.10,0:12:17.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那么就接上电源吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.80,0:12:18.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.21,0:12:20.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.05,0:12:26.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.54,0:12:29.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你…  好…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.28,0:12:32.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.25,0:12:35.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}我…  名…  叫…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.78,0:12:39.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}与…  四…  郎…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.93,0:12:37.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  海
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.34,0:12:40.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如何  这孩子能好好开口说话了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.91,0:12:41.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,「好好」啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.82,0:12:46.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}是…  大…  家…  的…  朋…  友…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.99,0:12:45.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小淳？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.38,0:12:53.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}机…  器…  人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.57,0:12:54.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.90,0:12:56.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的名字叫做与四郎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.79,0:12:58.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它是那个时候的…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.99,0:13:01.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小亚希  快关掉机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.58,0:13:02.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.78,0:13:06.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\fs22}是…  朋…  友…  哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.33,0:13:05.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.26,0:13:09.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你才不是我的朋友呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.61,0:13:11.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊  淳
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.50,0:13:24.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(280,185)\fs18\1c000000\bord0\b1}退\N部\N申\N请\N书
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.75,0:13:24.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她终于来这一招了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.55,0:13:26.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,唉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.39,0:13:29.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我有点事  就先走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.13,0:13:30.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.22,0:13:32.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在这么关键的时刻  你这是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.17,0:13:34.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不管淳的事情了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.19,0:13:37.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是让你暂且冷静一下静观其变吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.12,0:13:40.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,推不开的门就拉拉看  欲擒故纵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.85,0:13:44.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这不是恋爱的格言吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.60,0:13:50.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨姐姐  我的正拳打得怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.82,0:13:52.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿咻  嘿咻
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.38,0:13:55.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是让你别再叫我笨姐姐了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.90,0:13:57.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明明是我的踢腿比较厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.65,0:14:00.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐姐姐  再做些点心带来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.21,0:14:01.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.91,0:14:03.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.36,0:14:04.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.61,0:14:11.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和你平时给人的感觉完全不同呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.08,0:14:14.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为我平时都很紧张
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.67,0:14:16.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要退出Robo部吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.72,0:14:18.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.05,0:14:20.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我果然还是不行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.10,0:14:22.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我害怕机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.22,0:14:27.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还是不要帮忙给爷爷打气比较好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.81,0:14:33.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我倒是觉得只有小淳你能让DOKU振作起来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.73,0:14:34.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么会呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.47,0:14:37.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一直都在避开他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.16,0:14:39.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他肯定还在生我的气吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.10,0:14:41.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他一定觉得我这个孙女很讨厌
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.61,0:14:46.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,DOKU的机器人的线缆都被切断了对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.15,0:14:48.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道那是为什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.76,0:14:50.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.34,0:14:53.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这是掉在仓库里的照片
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.48,0:14:56.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.24,0:14:58.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要不要再考虑一下
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.69,0:15:12.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机器人啊  可是人类的好朋友哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.47,0:15:18.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那  我也是它们的朋友啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.84,0:15:21.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,当然  哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.99,0:15:32.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊？  Gun制造1号机的视频？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.93,0:15:33.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是…是的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.18,0:15:36.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给你  就是这个
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.95,0:15:38.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,非…非常感谢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.08,0:15:43.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哇  好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.07,0:15:46.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好大
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.38,0:15:49.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,逊毙了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.22,0:15:51.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好大
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.50,0:15:53.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大归大  但逊毙了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.33,0:15:55.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就没有什么武器吗  武器
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.24,0:15:57.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他们看起来好开心
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.65,0:16:00.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家原来都是这样看待机器人的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.20,0:16:03.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好慢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.03,0:16:05.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样算是在走吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.72,0:16:13.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,机器人啊  可是人类的好朋友哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.68,0:16:22.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,DOKU一直都在自责
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.87,0:16:28.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他说自己居然自大地认为机器人是人类的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.76,0:16:33.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不过老师倒觉得他的这种想法才是自以为是
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.36,0:16:36.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这可是小常识哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.38,0:16:36.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.75,0:16:39.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.53,0:16:45.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.11,0:16:48.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,DOKU瘦了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.67,0:16:52.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你能跟我们去一趟机器人诊所吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.56,0:16:55.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那家店已经关门大吉了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.51,0:16:58.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而且原本就赚不了钱
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.62,0:17:00.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么能说这种违心话呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.39,0:17:03.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的内心肯定是非常喜欢它的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.91,0:17:06.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也最喜欢Gunvarrel了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.14,0:17:08.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以无论发生什么都要努力完成它
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.69,0:17:09.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.13,0:17:11.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,总之  我已经…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.14,0:17:14.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,DOKU的机器人们可是在等着你回去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.55,0:17:16.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.44,0:17:17.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你做了些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.54,0:17:19.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们  难道说…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.21,0:17:22.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不过是重现了一下机器人诊所刚开业时的盛况罢了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.15,0:17:25.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,笨蛋  你们都干了些什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.46,0:17:29.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就亲眼来确认一下我们是不是傻瓜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.46,0:17:34.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已经帮你申请好外出许可了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.09,0:17:36.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.33,0:18:02.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.25,0:18:05.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我住手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.13,0:18:06.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.50,0:18:08.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不然又会伤害到人的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.38,0:18:13.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又会让人留下可怕的回忆
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.68,0:18:16.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我让那孩子…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.37,0:18:20.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我…我让淳她…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.99,0:18:45.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,与四郎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.24,0:18:48.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.79,0:18:51.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的名字叫做与四郎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.50,0:18:55.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是大家的朋友——机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.89,0:18:57.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来和我握握手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.32,0:19:02.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,来和我握握手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.00,0:19:04.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藤田爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.03,0:19:09.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你怎么会知道我的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.02,0:19:11.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为有人教会了它
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.07,0:19:16.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是你的孙女亲自教会了你的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.79,0:19:19.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,孙女…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.67,0:19:38.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,请多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.73,0:19:41.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,藤田爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.66,0:19:45.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你愿意原谅我吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.30,0:19:49.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,应该道歉的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.44,0:19:52.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,对不起  爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.41,0:19:55.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,虽然我还是有那么一点害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.08,0:20:03.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但今后我会努力再次喜欢上与四郎君和其他的孩子们的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.82,0:20:06.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定会和它们再次成为好朋友的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.89,0:20:08.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.50,0:20:11.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您一定要快点好起来啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.01,0:20:12.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.41,0:20:18.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.59,0:20:20.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.08,0:20:35.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.71,0:20:45.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那  我们就回去了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.07,0:20:48.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别太乱来  好好养病啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.55,0:20:51.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我还没老到需要你来操心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.18,0:20:54.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看你这么精神应该是没问题了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.13,0:20:55.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.72,0:21:00.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你们还在制作那个什么巨型机器人吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.51,0:21:02.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那还用说吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.06,0:21:05.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等我出院了  就让我瞧一瞧吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.59,0:21:09.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,让我看看它够不够Rock
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.40,0:21:10.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.55,0:21:11.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊哈哈
